long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AirQuery Augmatica is a Smart Look Up Business Intelligence search technology for specific information for specific users for specific functions.

AirQuery is a modern BI SAAS information platform with comprehensive coverage of all aspects of Reporting
and Analytics. 

AirQuery allows users to work on Data modeling for building Symantec layers, Dashboards and Data Operation
by building SQL queries.

With AirQuery account organization can access their data in multiple SAAS applications without relying on any one, and this is multi fold productivity.
